212
00:09:10,050 --> 00:09:10,990
Come here.

213
00:09:11,090 --> 00:09:14,020
Only traps descend from above.

214
00:09:14,140 --> 00:09:15,000
We have it all.

215
00:09:15,000 --> 00:09:17,650
Riches are never easily gained.

216
00:09:17,780 --> 00:09:21,240
Always stay alert and never forget.

217
00:09:21,600 --> 00:09:22,720
Did you hear that clearly?

218
00:09:22,720 --> 00:09:23,840
Say it again.

219
00:09:25,210 --> 00:09:28,120
Keep family matters hidden.

220
00:09:28,360 --> 00:09:31,590
Guard your gold and silver well.

221
00:09:31,840 --> 00:09:35,270
Be cautious in correspondence.

222
00:09:35,550 --> 00:09:38,960
(Do not mistake him; Lord Sun is here)
Double-check before paying.

223
00:09:46,150 --> 00:09:46,990
Next,

224
00:09:47,320 --> 00:09:48,750
The Voyage to Haihun Band

225
00:09:48,940 --> 00:09:50,200
will present a song for you all,

226
00:09:50,320 --> 00:09:51,840
"Bewitching Incense is Poisonous".

227
00:09:52,540 --> 00:09:53,750
Great!

228
00:09:53,910 --> 00:09:55,120
Friends,

229
00:09:55,200 --> 00:09:57,480
