I just taught you?

230
00:09:57,720 --> 00:10:00,790
Wow, oh, oh.

231
00:10:01,150 --> 00:10:03,360
I can already feel your excitement.

232
00:10:03,360 --> 00:10:04,260
So next,

233
00:10:04,270 --> 00:10:06,840
