Let's fire it up!

235
00:10:08,200 --> 00:10:12,410
Oh, oh, oh.

236
00:10:13,820 --> 00:10:14,680
What are you doing?

237
00:10:14,690 --> 00:10:15,680
Hurry up.

238
00:10:16,080 --> 00:10:16,960
I'm nervous...

239
00:10:17,510 --> 00:10:18,550
It's a small gig.

240
00:10:18,550 --> 00:10:19,730
What's a Marquis got to fear?

241
00:10:19,730 --> 00:10:20,600
Come on.

242
00:10:20,600 --> 00:10:23,260
Sing, come on, sing.

243
00:10:23,270 --> 00:10:24,420
Give us one, give us one!

244
00:10:26,630 --> 00:10:27,960
