245
00:10:27,960 --> 00:10:28,800
You can do it.

246
00:10:29,440 --> 00:10:30,630
Come on.

247
00:10:30,630 --> 00:10:34,240
Sing, sing!

248
00:10:34,730 --> 00:10:35,590
Alright.

249
00:10:35,880 --> 00:10:36,730
Let's go.

250
