♪Say no to illusion, no to false gods♪

282
00:12:49,150 --> 00:12:52,260
♪Mishenfu must be discarded♪

283
00:12:52,360 --> 00:12:56,480
♪Mishenfu must be gone forever♪

284
00:13:00,210 --> 00:13:02,300
Rock and roll never dies.

285
00:13:06,590 --> 00:13:07,690
He suddenly collapsed.

286
00:13:07,720 --> 00:13:08,960
Is this how rock and roll he is?

287
00:13:16,840 --> 00:13:18,440
Good thing I made it back in time.

288
00:13:18,720 --> 00:13:19,630
Or else…

289
00:13:21,190 --> 00:13:22,200
He's going to be fine.

290
00:13:22,200 --> 00:13:23,790
He's hardly gotten sick since childhood.

291
00:13:24,630 --> 00:13:25,910
This sudden fainting

292
00:13:26,550 --> 00:13:28,390
must be the aftereffects of poisoning.

293
00:13:28,720 --> 00:13:31,080
It's my fault, I was too careless.

294
00:13:31,430 --> 00:13:32,750
This has nothing to do with you.

295
00:13:32,960 --> 00:13:34,030
Don't blame yourself.

296
00:13:34,340 --> 00:13:35,870
I'm the one who knows him best.

297
00:13:36,200 --> 00:13:40,170
So well I can tell his mood
from his first word.

298
00:13:40,480 --> 00:13:42,750
One step from him
and I know where he's going.

299
00:13:43,660 --> 00:13:45,560
Someone poisoned him,

300
00:13:46,370 --> 00:13:48,010
yet I didn't notice a single thing.

301
00:13:48,270 --> 00:13:50,110
I even thought
it was his bottled-up grief.

302
00:13:51,120 --> 00:13:52,360
That's what everyone thinks

303
00:13:52,610 --> 00:13:54,120
because he's been through a lot.

304
00:13:56,330 --> 00:13:58,090
We know each other too well.

305
00:13:58,720 --> 00:14:00,750
So well that day after day,

306
00:14:01,600 --> 00:14:04,600
the spark we once felt
have faded away.

307
00:14:05,250 --> 00:14:08,670
What's left is a self-assured sense
of knowing.

308
00:14:11,390 --> 00:14:12,630
Sometimes I wonder,

309
00:14:13,440 --> 00:14:14,480
between the Marquis and me,

310
00:14:14,850 --> 00:14:16,350
is it truly love that binds us

311
00:14:17,510 --> 00:14:18,790
or simply the habit of kinship?

312
00:14:21,030 --> 00:14:23,750
Whether it's love or kinship,

313
00:14:24,540 --> 00:14:25,380
it's an affection.

314
00:14:26,320 --> 00:14:29,000
Right now, you stay by each other's side.

315
00:14:29,430 --> 00:14:31,370
That's the most precious thing.

316
00:14:33,870 --> 00:14:35,700
The Marquis has been too weary lately

317
00:14:36,410 --> 00:14:38,100
and got emotional.

318
00:14:38,390 --> 00:14:39,340
You need not worry.

319
00:14:41,840 --> 00:14:42,790
De Jiu,

320
00:14:43,030 --> 00:14:44,790
after spending so much time with Wang,

321
00:14:45,030 --> 00:14:46,480
you've learned to comfort people.

322
00:14:49,440 --> 00:14:50,290
And you?

323
00:14:50,620 --> 00:14:51,860
How are things between you two?

324
00:14:52,240 --> 00:14:53,870
Has he confessed his feelings yet?

325
00:14:56,900 --> 00:14:57,910
To him,

326
00:14:58,790 --> 00:15:00,000
we're just comrades-in-arms.

327
00:15:00,360 --> 00:15:01,570
And to you?

328
00:15:05,500 --> 00:15:07,120
Master has raised me since childhood.

329
00:15:07,790 --> 00:15:09,960
Without Master, there would be no me.

330
00:15:10,750 --> 00:15:12,600
The duty entrusted by Master and Uncle

331
00:15:12,600 --> 00:15:14,120
is to protect Crown Prince's bloodline.

332
00:15:16,000 --> 00:15:17,440
Not only have I failed in my duty,

333
00:15:17,670 --> 00:15:19,370
but I dragged His Majesty into helping.

334
00:15:19,960 --> 00:15:21,120
Now Xiqiang are invading,

335
00:15:21,120 --> 00:15:22,270
and the borders are in peril.

336
00:15:22,550 --> 00:15:24,440
If I can't help His Majesty
restore peace,

337
00:15:24,600 --> 00:15:26,150
how can I speak of matters of the heart?

338
00:15:27,270 --> 00:15:28,180
De Jiu,

339
00:15:28,360 --> 00:15:29,790
just follow your heart.

340
00:15:30,440 --> 00:15:32,240
I'm glad you came back this time.

341
00:15:32,510 --> 00:15:34,440
Usually I only see them chattering away.

342
00:15:34,650 --> 00:15:36,550
Now, I have someone I can truly talk to.

343
00:15:37,790 --> 00:15:38,630
Madam.

344
00:15:38,990 --> 00:15:39,830
Madam.

345
00:15:40,100 --> 00:15:41,200
His Lordship is awake.

346
00:15:41,870 --> 00:15:42,710
Let's go.

347
00:15:44,730 --> 00:15:45,570
Your hand.

348
00:15:52,720 --> 00:15:53,780
Don't worry, it's fine.

349
00:16:12,850 --> 00:16:14,120
You're all here.

350
00:16:16,840 --> 00:16:17,680
Marquis.

351
00:16:26,790 --> 00:16:28,750
What I'm going to say next

352
00:16:30,480 --> 00:16:31,780
is of great importance.

353
00:16:33,200 --> 00:16:35,150
Why does it sound like a last will?

354
00:16:35,510 --> 00:16:36,680
I know my own body

355
00:16:37,990 --> 00:16:39,720
better than anyone.

356
00:16:41,080 --> 00:16:41,920
Heng.

357
00:16:42,870 --> 00:16:46,440
Please write down everything I say.

358
00:16:47,280 --> 00:16:49,920
These are things to be buried with me.

359
00:16:51,080 --> 00:16:52,220
It can't be that bad.

360
00:16:55,790 --> 00:16:56,670
Marquis.

361
00:16:59,050 --> 00:17:00,080
In my lifetime

362
00:17:01,840 --> 00:17:03,750
I've achieved little of real merit.

363
00:17:05,780 --> 00:17:07,600
But I wish to try another way.

364
00:17:09,830 --> 00:17:11,280
A way to give this world

365
00:17:12,700 --> 00:17:14,020
something to remember me by.

366
00:17:16,030 --> 00:17:17,630
These burial treasures

367
00:17:18,550 --> 00:17:19,760
are from me, Liu He.

368
00:17:19,770 --> 00:17:25,630
They're the only mark
I can leave on history.

369
00:17:32,280 --> 00:17:33,160
Heng,

370
00:17:35,230 --> 00:17:37,240
can you understand how I feel?

371
00:17:39,440 --> 00:17:40,310
Alright, alright.

372
00:17:40,640 --> 00:17:42,450
I'll write it down for you, every bit.

373
00:17:57,400 --> 00:17:58,510
First on the list,

374
00:17:59,920 --> 00:18:01,200
the ink-inscribed gold ingot.

375
00:18:03,750 --> 00:18:04,790
The amount

376
00:18:07,010 --> 00:18:07,920
to be decided.

377
00:18:12,730 --> 00:18:14,620
Everyone knows my wealth is vast.

378
00:18:15,980 --> 00:18:17,240
And this item

379
00:18:18,410 --> 00:18:21,960
is the very symbol of my title
as Haihun Marquis.

380
00:18:22,370 --> 00:18:23,510
Rest assured,

381
00:18:23,830 --> 00:18:26,140
the generations to come
will never forget you.

382
00:18:26,400 --> 00:18:27,920
Your name is known to almost everyone.

383
00:18:29,440 --> 00:18:30,280
Truly?

384
00:18:30,590 --> 00:18:31,430
Mm.

385
00:18:47,110 --> 00:18:49,510
♪Watch the storm;
hear the night rain fall♪

386
00:18:49,510 --> 00:18:51,110
♪Till the light of dawn♪

387
00:18:51,110 --> 00:18:52,830
♪A truth that cannot be spoken♪

388
00:18:53,510 --> 00:18:55,190
♪Right and wrong matter♪

389
00:18:55,190 --> 00:18:57,310
♪Yet I can't make the right choice♪

390
00:18:57,510 --> 00:18:58,950
♪The lost player in the game♪

391
00:18:59,190 --> 00:19:02,310
♪Made a move by a twist of fate♪

392
00:19:02,310 --> 00:19:04,830
♪The way back is lost,
leaving nowhere to return♪

393
00:19:04,830 --> 00:19:08,070
♪Borrow the endless cycles♪

394
00:19:08,630 --> 00:19:12,110
♪To fight for the most perfect outcome♪

395
00:19:12,870 --> 00:19:15,230
♪How to trace the threads
and follow cause and effect♪

396
00:19:15,230 --> 00:19:18,990
♪Seeking a strategy without flaw♪

397
00:19:19,270 --> 00:19:23,910
♪How to break free
from this fated yet unforeseen lock♪

398
00:19:24,070 --> 00:19:29,110
♪To live so as to shake the world♪

399
00:19:29,470 --> 00:19:33,590
♪With this journey,
I gain a fiercer edge♪

400
00:19:33,710 --> 00:19:35,790
♪I've planned
before I act countless times♪

401
00:19:35,870 --> 00:19:42,230
♪Fatal danger turned into a jest♪

402
00:19:42,350 --> 00:19:46,550
♪Through this road,
I watch the endless rise and fall♪

403
00:19:46,590 --> 00:19:48,670
♪In the chapters lie ages
of decay and bloom♪

404
00:19:48,670 --> 00:19:50,590
♪Let us meet again♪

405
00:19:50,600 --> 00:19:55,950
♪One hurried path, and one at ease♪

